  ],
  "remarks": "Tatyana Litvinenko is a major shareholder of PhosAgro, a globally leading producer of phosphate fertilisers. Russia is the world’s leading exporter of fertilisers, a sector which provides substantial revenue to the Russian Government. Tatyana Litvinenko is therefore a businessperson involved in an economic sector providing a substantial source of revenue to the Government of the Russian Federation, which is responsible for the annexation of Crimea and the destabilisation of Ukraine.",
